    "description": "<p>This spell creates a mobile, 20 foot diameter sphere of energy around the caster that prevents the entrance of plant creatures or animated plants. The shell is transparent, but it is not invisible. It moves with the caster. This spell may be used only defensively, not aggressively. An attempt to force the shell against a creature normally kept at bay by the spell causes the shell to collapse.</p>",
